	<div class="row infinite-scroll-item">

	<div class="article-card article-card-sm medium-4 columns first ">
		<a href="http://grist.org/climate-energy/understanding-obamas-suckiness-on-climate/"><!--[if lt IE 9]><img width="660" height="371" src="https://grist.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/silhouettepotus.jpg?w=660" class="attachment-large wp-post-image" alt="Obama" /><![endif]--><img src="https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/themes/vip/grist-foundation/img/grist-placeholder-image.png" class="ie-hide article-card-img no-js-hide" data-interchange="[https://grist.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/silhouettepotus.jpg?w=320&amp;h=180&amp;crop=1, (default)], [https://grist.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/silhouettepotus.jpg?w=480&amp;h=270&amp;crop=1, (only screen and (min-width: 1px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.5))]"><noscript><img src="https://grist.files.wordpress.com/2015/02/silhouettepotus.jpg?w=480&#038;h=270&#038;crop=1"></noscript></a>
